data.description: Welcome to this Retreat like no other in Meridian Ranch. This home features 4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. Both bedrooms on the main level have personal En suites for your convenience and the Primary bedroom features a custom closet and Spa Shower.  As you enter the home you will notice the spacious Voyer and beautiful arch ways leading to the living room. The Living Room is warm and inviting with its vaulted ceilings and large windows overlooking the backyard. The kitchen is a chef's dream that is equipped with a gas range, wall oven and microwave, dishwasher, and a HUGE island that is great for many to gather. The walk in Pantry is a great size to house all the goodies and Costco items with room to spare. As you come from the garage you will notice the spacious laundry room that has a nice size washing sink and mud room area. The basement has been completely renovated and features a nice dry bar and. Check out the upgraded LVP flooring, 9ft basement height and the additional 2 bedrooms and full bath. This basement has plenty of space for the whole family and an area that can be used for an office. Don't forget to check out the backyard oasis.
